description.en-us: Pavement Pounders was the name for the second series of transport trucks and included bonus vehicles that ran from late 1999 to 2003, coming after Long Haulers and before Truckin' Transporters , Racing Rigs , and Super Rigs .  See also Kool Toyz Racing Packs , Super Race Rigs and Wild Race Teams , playsets that included Pavement Pounders.
